Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:18.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,100)\fad(500,00)}「出现了！  因为是战斗少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是玉响咖啡厅的特制午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们两人的份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就把剩下的端来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的玉响午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得这午餐平时总是卖到脱销呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有这么丰富的菜式呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪惠和麻音时间上来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像记得你们午后要去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「没关系」  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然比起买东西  美味的玉响午餐更重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这午餐很宝贵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天小啪提前拜托妈妈才终于能吃到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小啪亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你们能高兴就再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也是第一次见的新品午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐碟和装点都很精致  看上去真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香亲来帮忙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  香亲  这午餐就由纪惠姐姐收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  等很久了  等得我腿都软了……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  香亲的推荐料理是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真会说啊   香亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  那就全部一口气吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香  来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我也有个那样可爱的弟弟就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的老哥完全不可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么个哥哥一点都不会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我觉得不想错过「看上去很好吃」的这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完之后的也要拍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得或许还留着「看上去很好吃」的这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜点是蜜桃果冻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃  看上去就凉凉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口吃上去蜜桃的香味就扩散开来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这好像不是普通的果冻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着放了点葛根粉  有点和风的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵软香滑好有夏天的感觉  好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我这个的做法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  礼拜六下午怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是饭后茶  请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  香亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个茶纪惠姐姐我就收下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  香亲端来的茶最好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯  请务必亲手帮我倒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太来劲了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香亲  再见喽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然比起哥哥  人生就该有个弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人跟来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你这家伙难道是小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是难道  我就是小学生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我的名字叫做小町  不叫做你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  小町妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跟着我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是所谓的跟踪狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是监视哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了保证你不再继续做坏事的才隐蔽监视的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是暴露了的话  就不叫做隐蔽监视了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  真是变幻莫测的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你输了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再比一次  行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  已经分出胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然输了就要听我的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了我没输嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来比一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被她同化了  纪惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非得监视纪惠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的诡计我全部看穿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  诡计？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我可是知道你为了讨好香君而特意去学甜点的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…香？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非得像你说的那样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你还装蒜吗  明明都输给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再比一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心的话  就试着来追我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪惠  你把买东西的事忘了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最近的份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前午餐的照片吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么让你在意的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  总觉得拍得不像我想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍得食物看上去感觉好吃可不是件容易事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maestro好像有在拍店里的食物照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么诀窍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好试着着重于光影的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  重要的是那种「很好吃」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先试吃一下  然后融入「很好吃」的感觉来摄影或许会比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吃掉了不就不能摄影了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不靠谱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  接下来你打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  好像今天纪惠要来玉响咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去玉响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  蜜桃的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为约好了要奶奶教我之前那新款甜点的制作方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰亲也会去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫我薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  小香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来请教这之前那款甜点的制作方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是跟香同年级的小町妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是纪惠认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是认识还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是正义的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会阻止你的诡计的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  久等了  这是玫瑰果茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  味道真好闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色好美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫你这家伙  我叫小町
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  我就算了  要是给奶奶添麻烦就不好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添麻烦的是你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假装向奶奶学甜点的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却去讨好香君  好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来比一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我究竟谁能做出更好吃的甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来场甜点胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一决高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西不能拿来比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经认输了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才会输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被小学生牵着鼻子走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们俩就在这儿做甜点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就用做出来的东西来决胜负怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来判定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香回来的话就让他来试吃判定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  好像准备完成了  预备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪惠你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜桃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜桃果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那个好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要向奶奶学的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  并不是奶奶的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先按照自己的做法来试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是以西点师为目标的纪惠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小町还没决定要做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我能做的东西太多了  好难决定…呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  小町你喜欢薄烤饼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就试着做下薄烤饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然奶奶这样说的话我就做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正等下要搅拌的  没有打好也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放点糖好好搅拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  起白沫了就放牛奶进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来放香草液和酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一起混合搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面粉要振动着撒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搅拌的时候不要犹豫  干脆一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有结块就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶的薄烤饼我和小香都很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町  差不多要翻面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多用一个锅铲比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点糊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微烤过头了点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  真遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为薄烤饼什么的很简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无论什么甜点  想要做得好吃就有一件不能忘记的重要事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好想给别人带来美味」的那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是最重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在很努力地做着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来并不是想讨好香君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来也要加油哦  小町
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  该翻面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町妹妹  笑得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「好想给别人带来美味」的那种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的要给香吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我再从头开始做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想给香君吃成品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  那就开始准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町是什么时候开始在意香的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  4月的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香搬来的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始还以为他是女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他是男孩子之后吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就开始在意起他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  凉下来后就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个也能烤好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做甜点时最重要的事情  小町你不是已经掌握了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外观上两边都合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  平常都是这个时间回的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小町你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你…好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香  两个都吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就从薄烤饼开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个我也开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么胜负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香  两边都很好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多的程度？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打成平手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我都能吃完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也来吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  尽情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说「好吃」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个果冻  明明也是用的蜜桃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉味道和奶奶做的那种不同  还真是独特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用皮和核来勾出味和色是要点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  纪惠为什么要决定学做甜点的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别催我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有一次我突然发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭旅行都因此取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得是因为我才取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥一定会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}二重烧，正式名称是今川烧，别名大判烧，回转烧，太鼓馒。豆沙馅的烤饼。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是二重烧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二重烧是纪惠喜欢的食物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是哥哥喜欢的食物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是觉得自己喜欢的东西谁都会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那时候吃的二重烧的味道忘不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想肯定是希望让人露出笑容的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把甜点变得甜蜜可口了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜的东西是用温馨的感觉做成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗  小町
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有着很温馨的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才抱着「好想给别人带来美味」的心情而努力的小町
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的露出了很温柔的笑脸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃呢  薄烤饼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话  好像能拍下有「很好吃」那种感觉的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是不是很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这张
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好想给别人带来美味」的那份温柔情感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够给甜点带来甜蜜美味的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么东西能够给照片带来美妙的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味的东西能给制作的人和品尝的人都带来笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拍的照片若有一天能做到那样  就太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来比一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.08,0:24:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用照片来讨好很卑鄙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.22,0:24:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  玉响～hitotose～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.27,0:24:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因为是在等待涨潮的小岛听到的声音」
